Depends: R (>= 3.0.2), lattice (>= 0.20-27), latticeExtra (>= 0.6-26), cluster (>= 1.14.4), hexbin (>= 1.26.3), BoutrosLab.utilities (>= 1.9.5), BoutrosLab.statistics.general (>= 2.1.1), BoutrosLab.dist.overload (>= 1.0.1), grid
Imports: gridExtra,  tools, gtable, e1071, MASS(>= 7.3-29)
